# puppet-openlava

Puppet module for Openlava client and server

## Usage

To use this module simply include `openlava` class for the hosts on which you wish to install openlava.

```
class { openlava:
	version => '2.0',
	download_location => '/opt/',
}
```

###Parameters

This is not exhaustive but will cover most of the parameters you can set for this class.

## Development

### Testing

Testing requires the following dependencies:

* rake
* bundler

Install gem dependencies

    bundle install

Run unit tests

    bundle exec rake test
